Package com.tomas.cubesolver.neuralnetwork

Package defining neural network with it's evaluation and training using back propagation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Solve
    The Solve object is one that can be mapped to a input and output, such as the input and output neurons of a neural network.
    Train
    The interface for objects that can be trained using a training algorithm as stochastic back propagation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackPropagation
    Training algorithm that works by repeatedly changing edge weights to decreasing error It can train objects implementing Train interface
    NN
    Class that defines neural network and it's functions
    TrainData
    Class representing one line of training data that are generated and saved to file using other classes

Package com.tomas.cubesolver.neuralnetwork Description

Package defining neural network with it's evaluation and training using back propagation. It does not work with actual cube but with Solve interface so that it is more portable and can be used not only for rubic cube but for the neural network computing XOR operation as well
